NAME
    Template::Plugin::Octets - TT2 plugin to format numeric values as binary
    octets

VERSION
    version 0.16

SYNOPSIS
        [% USE Octets %]

        Xmit [% Octets.kio(100500) -%] Kio
        Recv [% Octets.mio(9000) -%] Mio

        # Output:
        # Xmit 98.1 Kio
        # Recv ~0 Mio

DESCRIPTION
    Template::Plugin::Octets is a plugin for Template Toolkit v2, which
    allows you to format numbers in templates.

METHODS
    kio Format value as kibioctets (2^10 octets).

    mio Format value as mebioctets (2^20 octets).

    gio Format value as gibioctets (2^30 octets).

SEE ALSO
    Template

    Template::Plugin::Procedural

